## 🔄 Quick Reset Script

Create a `reset.ps1` file in your project directory:

```powershell
#!/usr/bin/env powershell

Write-Host "Resetting YouTube to MP3 Converter..." -ForegroundColor Green

# Clean up
clean-pycache

# Recreate virtual environment
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force venv -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
python -m venv venv

# Activate and install
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt

Write-Host "Reset complete! Run 'python app.py' to start." -ForegroundColor Green
```

